  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的架构图，核心是三层结构：ROS2层作为MQTT Broker集群，中间HWI层做边缘节点，最下面是Hardware层的PLC和边缘设备。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "HWI",
        "Hardware"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，ROS2层是MQTT Broker集群，那这一层需要几个节点？另外HWI层的SI节点是做什么用的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ROS2层放三个Broker节点，叫C1、C2、C3，做负载均衡。HWI层的SI是边缘节点的核心服务接口，负责聚合下面Hardware层的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以C1、C2、C3三个Broker都连到SI，SI再向下连接Hardware层的设备。Hardware层具体有哪些？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "Hardware"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Hardware层需要三个：M1是PLC逻辑控制器，M2和M3是两个边缘计算节点，都通过SI做数据交换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "PLC",
        "EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已创建三个子图：ROS2包含C1-C3，HWI包含SI，Hardware包含M1-M3。现在画连接关系，C1、C2、C3都单向指向SI对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "subgraph",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Broker到SI是单向数据下发。但SI到M1、M2、M3是双向的，因为既要采集PLC数据，又要下发控制指令。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连接画好了。不过有个问题，HWI层的标签我写的是'IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode'，但里面的SI节点也是MQTT Broker，这和ROS2层的Broker会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确实，SI虽然是Broker，但在架构里它是边缘节点的组件，标签保持EdgeNode更准确。不过等等，Hardware层的M2、M3标签应该也是EdgeNode，M1是PLC_Logic，这样区分清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "修正了，M1标注为PLC_Logic，M2和M3标注为EdgeNode。但发现Hardware子图的标签我写成了MQTT_Broker，这应该是EdgeNode的汇总层，需要改吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
