      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "Hardware子图的标签确实错了，应该是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode，表示这是边缘设备层。另外ROS2子图的标签应该是MQTT_Broker集群。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "ROS2",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复标签。现在检查连接：C1、C2、C3单向到SI，SI双向到M1、M2、M3。不过SI在HWI子图里，标签显示MQTT_Broker，但实际功能是边缘节点接口，这样展示可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "HWI",
