      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构确认：ROS2子图（MQTT_Broker）含C1-C3，HWI子图（EdgeNode）含SI，Hardware子图（EdgeNode）含M1-M3。连接关系也确认无误。需要调整布局方向吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
