      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "布局已调整为TB。最终检查：三个子图标签分别是MQTT_Broker、EdgeNode、EdgeNode；C1-C3到SI是单向线，SI到M1-M3是双向线。还有需要调整的吗？",
